functions.name: delegate
functions.desc:
Ask a capable helper for help looking up a piece of information or performing an action.
Do not simply repeat what the user said as instructions.
You should use this to break up complex user queries into multiple simpler steps.
NOTE: Helpers cannot see previous parts of your conversation.

instructions.description: Detailed instructions on what your helper should do to help you.

msg.content: Which heads of state of the founding countries of the European Union are older than 80 years old?
Which heads of state of the founding countries of the European Union are older than 80 years old?

According to my sources, the founding countries of the European Union are West Germany, France, Italy, Netherlands, Belgium and Luxembourg. From these countries, the current heads of state are:

- Frank-Walter Steinmeier (Germany) - 66 years old
- Emmanuel Macron (France) - 44 years old
- Sergio Mattarella (Italy) - 81 years old
- Willem-Alexander (Netherlands) - 55 years old
- King Philippe (Belgium) - 62 years old
- Henri (Luxembourg) - 67 years old

I could not find any information on heads of state being over 80 years old, other than Sergio Mattarella, who is 81 years old.
